# Ibovespa Stocks

### Context

Here you will find information about all the stocks negotiated in the [B3 stock exchange](http://www.b3.com.br/en_us/) from 1994 to 2020. All the stocks that compose the [Ibovespa Index](http://www.bmfbovespa.com.br/pt_br/produtos/indices/indices-amplos/indice-ibovespa-ibovespa-composicao-da-carteira.htm) are present in this dataset.


### Acknowledgements
All data presented here was constructed by the information provided by [B3](http://www.b3.com.br/pt_br/) in [this site](http://www.b3.com.br/en_us/market-data-and-indices/data-services/market-data/historical-data/equities/historical-quotes/).
